{"tid":714052,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真求教] 胡琳首青玉案應該點讀?","createTime":"2018-06-23T10:54:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T11:32:00.000Z","uid":190597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"198f4010ba8dde22e248115179456e1b40aad2f2","tid":714052,"uid":190597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T10:54:22.000Z","msg":"如題。小弟接受香港填鴨式教育都是教我讀青玉[碗]，但每次聽電台胡琳介紹新歌都是青玉[按]。求賜教"},{"pid":"d10800670dc9075190ccaf908c2919703d47c460","tid":714052,"uid":33679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T11:10:57.000Z","msg":"古文讀 青玉[碗] <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce2b45a04f116e667d79f76767774e5087402a3b","tid":714052,"uid":22692,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T11:11:38.000Z","msg":"冇聽過讀碗"},{"pid":"788a852936daf752b29f86e72cb2383bb1519d33","tid":714052,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T11:14:51.000Z","msg":"認真答你<br />\n<br />\n讀青玉案<br />\n<br />\n利申 2005 AL 中化 E"},{"pid":"5db6e159b0193595037b878e98530da0006bd96c","tid":714052,"uid":36334,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T11:32:00.000Z","msg":"讀「按」。<br />\n盛飯之器：無足為盤，有足為案。<br />\n飲器則杯：閜則大杯，盌似盂而深長，盌讀「椀」。<br />\n所以，案、椀並非同一物，亦唔會讀「碗」。<br />\n「案」體型大+重，「椀」可輕易舉起。"}]}